From: Andrei Radchenko <aradchen@redhat.com>
Subject: [PATCH] v8: include climits for CHAR_BIT in memcopy.h

CHAR_BIT is used in the NEON-optimized SimdMemCopy path on aarch64
but <climits> is not included, causing build failure.

diff --git a/deps/v8/src/base/memcopy.h b/deps/v8/src/base/memcopy.h
index 1111111..2222222 100644
--- a/deps/v8/src/base/memcopy.h
+++ b/deps/v8/src/base/memcopy.h
@@ -7,6 +7,7 @@

 #include <stdlib.h>

+#include <climits>
 #include <atomic>

 #include "include/v8config.h"
